023package org.opt4j.viewer;
024
025import static java.lang.annotation.ElementType.TYPE;
026import static java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME;
027
028import java.lang.annotation.Inherited;
029import java.lang.annotation.Retention;
030import java.lang.annotation.Target;
031
032/**
033 * The {@link ToolBarOrder} Annotation is used for {@link ToolBarService}
034 * ordering.
035 * 
036 * @see ToolBarService
037 * @author lukasiewycz
038 * 
039 */
040@Retention(RUNTIME)
041@Target(TYPE)
042@Inherited
043public @interface ToolBarOrder {
044
045        /**
046         * Returns the order priority.
047         * 
048         * @return the order priority
049         */
050        public int value();
051
052}
